      • loadLiveRegionServersAndInitializeListeners

        public final Set<ServerName> loadLiveRegionServersAndInitializeListeners()
                                                                  throws IOException
        Description copied from interface: ReplicationTracker
        In this method, you need to load the newest list of region server list and return it, and all later changes to the region server list must be passed to the listeners.

        This is very important for us to not miss a region server crash.

        Notice that this method can only be called once.

        Specified by:
        loadLiveRegionServersAndInitializeListeners in interface ReplicationTracker
        Returns:
        Set of region servers.
        Throws:
        IOException
